::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe runs as fast as he can away from the Cybertronian Fire, his 
cloaking device running out of power about a thousand feet away from the 
Maximal ship. He lets out a breath of relief. That had been a close one...

The assassing takes off running off toward the forest.
